io.micronaut.security.oauth2.endpoint.token.response

Class IdTokenLoginHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.micronaut.security.token.jwt.cookie.CookieLoginHandler
      • io.micronaut.security.oauth2.endpoint.token.response.IdTokenLoginHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LoginHandler, RedirectingLoginHandler

    @Requires(property="micronaut.security.authentication",
          value="idtoken")
 @Singleton
public class IdTokenLoginHandler
extends CookieLoginHandler
    Sets CookieLoginHandler`s cookie value to the idtoken received from an authentication provider. The cookie expiration is set to the expiration of the IDToken exp claim.
    Since:
    2.0.0
    Author:
    Sergio del Amo
